	mouse support for X11 and OS/2 PM. Implemented by Pieter-Tjerk de
	Boer <ptdeboer@cs.utwente.nl>, Petr Mikulik <mikulik@physics.muni.cz>,
	Johannes Zellner <johannes@zellner.org>.

